This Aint A Scene Its An Arms Race

version_description: All versions of this song contain significant errors. This version solves all of these problems, among many others not mentioned:  1: Third line of verses, missing C chord – 2: Third line of chorus, missing F chord – 3: Hook: A variety of chord placement and choice errors. Compare this version to the original song and to other versions, the improvements are significant.
From the album "Infinity on High" by Fall Out Boy, ideal for playing with vocals or some accompanyment. Good for Rhythm Guitar.
Simple chord progression, no capo, standard tuning, chords timed over all lyrics.
Version that can be played acoustically.
